hadiths[27]{hadithnumber,text}:
1040,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke suraj ko girahan lagna shuru hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (uth kar jaldi mein) chadar ghaseet'tey huey masjid mein gaey. sath hi ham bhi gaey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein 2 rakaat Namaz padhai yahan tak ki suraj saaf ho gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke suraj aur chaand mein girahan kisi ki maut w halaakat se nahi lagta lekin jab tum girahan dekho to us waqt Namaz aur dua kartey raho jab tak girahan khul na jaey.
1041,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya suraj aur chaand mein girahan kisi shakhs ki maut se nahi lagtaa. ye donon to Allah Taala ki qudrat ki nishaniyan hain. isliye usey dekhtey hi khadey ho jao aur Namaz padho .
1042,"nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya suraj aur chaand mein girahan kisi ki maut w zindagi se nahi lagta balke ye Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain, isliye jab tum ye dekho to Namaz padho."
1043,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein suraj girahan us din laga jis din (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahibzadey ( Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ka intiqal hua kuchh log kehney lagey ke girahan Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ki wjah se laga hai. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke girahan kisi ki maut w hayaat se nahi lagta . albatta tum jab usey dekho to Namaz padha karo aur dua kya karo.
1044,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein suraj girahan hua to aap ne logon ko Namaz padhai. pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey to badi der tak khadey rahe, qiyam ke baad rukoo kya aur rukoo mein bahut der tak rahe. phir rukoo se uthney ke baad der tak dobara khadey rahe lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pahley qiyam se kuchh kam, phir rukoo kya to badi der tak rukoo mein rahe lekin pahley se mukhtasar, phir sajde mein gaey aur der tak sajde ki haalat mein rahe. dusri rakaat mein bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah kya, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farigh huey to girahan khul chuka tha. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba diya Allah Taala ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya ke suraj aur chaand donon Allah ki nishaniyan hain aur kisi ki maut w hayaat se unmein girahan nahi lagtaa. jab tum girahan laga hua dekho to Allah se dua karo takbeer kaho aur Namaz padho aur sadqa karo. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey Muhammad ki ummat ke logo! dekho is baat par Allah Taala se zyada ghairat aur kisi ko nahi aati ke iska koi banda ya bandi zina karey, aey ummat Muhammad! Allah ki qism jo kuchh main janta hun agar tumhen bhi malum ho jaey to tum hanstey kam aur rotey zyada."
1045,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein suraj girahan laga to ye elaan kya gaya ke Namaz honey wali hai.
1046,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein suraj girahan laga, usi waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif le gaey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey saf baandhii Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne takbeer kahi aur bahut der Quran Majeed padhtey rahe phir takbeer kahi aur bahut lamba rukoo kya phir ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( keh kar khadey ho gaey aur sajda nahi kya ( rukoo se uthney ke baad) phir bahut der tak Quran Majeed padhtey rahe. lekin pehli qirat se kam, phir takbeer ke sath rukoo mein chaley gaey aur der tak rukoo mein rahe, ye rukoo bhi pahley rukoo se kam tha. ab ( سمع الله لمن حمده (aur ( ربنا ولك الحمد‏ ( kaha phir sajde mein gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dusri rakaat mein bhi isi tarah kya (un donon rakaton mein) poorey char rukoo aur char sajdey kiye. Namaz se farigh honey se pahley hi suraj saaf ho chuka tha. Namaz ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar khutba farmaya aur pahley Allah Taala ki uski shaan ke mutabiq tareef ki phir farmaya ke suraj aur chaand Allah ki 2 nishaniyan hain unmein girahan kisi ki maut w hayaat ki wjah se nahi lagta lekin jab tum girahan dekha karo to fauran Namaz ki taraf lapko. Zohri ne kaha ke Kaseer-bin-Abbas apne bhai Abdullah-bin-Abbas se riwayat kartey they wo suraj girahan ka qissa is tarah bayan kartey they jaisey Urwa ne Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se naql kya. Zohri ne kaha maine Urwa se kaha tumharey bhai Abdullah-bin-Zubair ne jis din Madina mein suraj girahan hua subah ki Namaz ki tarah 2 rakaat padhi aur kuchh zyada nahi kya. unhon-ne kaha haan magar wo sunnat ke tareeq se chook gaey."
1047,"jis din suraj mein khusoof (girahan) laga to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey takbeer kahi phir der tak Quran Majeed padhtey rahe. lekin iske baad aik lamba rukoo kya. rukoo se sar uthaya to kaha ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pahley hi ki tarah khadey ho gaey aur der tak Quran Majeed padhtey rahe lekin us martaba ki qirat pahley se kuchh kam thi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein gaey aur bahut der tak sajde mein rahe phir dusri rakaat mein bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah kya, phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to suraj saaf ho chuka tha. Namaz se farigh ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba diya aur farmaya ke suraj aur chaand ka (kusoof) (girahan) Allah Taala ki aik nishani hai aur unmein (girahan) kisi ki maut w zindagi par nahi lagtaa. lekin jab tum se dekho to fauran Namaz ke liye lapko."
1048,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya suraj aur chaand donon Allah Taala ki nishaniyan hain aur kisi ki maut aur zindagi se unmein girahan nahi lagta balke Allah Taala iske zariey apne bandon ko daraata hai. abdul-Waaris, Shoba, Khalid-bin-Abdullaah aur Hammaad-bin-Salma un sab Haafizon ne Yunus se ye jumla ke'' Allah Taala unko girahan karke apne bandon ko daraataa hai ''bayaan nahi kya aur Yunus ke sath us hadis ko Musa ne mubaarak-bin-Fazaala se, unhon-ne imam Hasan Basri se riwayat kya. usmein yun hai ke Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sun kar mujh ko khabar di ke Allah Taala unko girahan karke apne bandon ko daraataa hai aur Yunus ke sath us hadis ko Asha's-bin-Abdullaah ne bhi imam Hasan Basri se riwayat kya."
1049,aik Yahudi aurat unke paas maangney ke liye aai aur us ne dua di ke Allah aapko qabr ke azab se bachaaey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke kya logon ko qabr mein azab hoga? is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Allah Taala ki us se panah mangta hun.
1050,"phir aik martaba subah ko (kahiin janey ke liye) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sawar huey iske baad suraj girahan laga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) din chadhey wapas huey aur apni beeviyon ke hujron se guzartey huey (masjid mein) Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki pairvi mein niyat baandh li. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bahut hi lamba qiyam kya phir rukoo bhi bahut lamba kya, iske baad khadey huey aur ab ki baar qiyam phir lamba kya lekin pahley se kuchh kam, phir rukoo kya aur us baar bhi der tak rukoo mein rahe lekin pahley rukoo se kuchh kam, phir rukoo se sar uthaya aur sajde mein gaey. ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) phir dobara khadey huey aur bahut der tak qiyam kya lekin pahley qiyam se kuchh kam, phir aik lamba rukoo kya lekin pahley rukoo se kuchh kam, phir rukoo se sar uthaya aur qiyam mein ab ki baar bhi bahut der tak rahe lekin pahley se kam der tak (chauthi martaba) phir rukoo kya aur bahut der tak rukoo mein rahe lekin pahley se mukhtasar. rukoo se sar uthaya to sajde mein chaley gaey aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is tarah Namaz poori kar li. iske baad Allah Taala ne jo chaha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya usi khutbe mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko hidayat farmai ke azaabe-qabr se Allah ki panah maangein."
1051,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein suraj ko girahan laga to elaan hua ke Namaz honey wali hai (is Namaz mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik rakaat mein 2 rukoo kiye aur phir dusri rakaat mein bhi 2 rukoo kiye, iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey rahe (Qa'da mein) yahan tak ke suraj saaf ho gaya. Abdullah ne kaha Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke maine us se zyada lamba sajda aur kabhi nahi kya."
1052,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein suraj ko girahan laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi thi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne itna lamba qiyam kya ke itni der mein sura al-Baqara padhi ja sakti thi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo lamba kya aur uske baad khadey huey to abki baar bhi qiyam bahut lamba tha lekin pahley se kuchh kam phir aik doosra lamba rukoo kya jo pahley rukoo se kuchh kam tha phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein gaey, sajde se uth kar phir lamba qiyam kya lekin pahley qiyam ke muqaabley mein kam lamba tha phir aik lamba rukoo kya. ye rukoo bhi pahley rukoo ke muqaabla mein kam tha rukoo se sar utha ne ke baad phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut der tak khadey rahe aur ye qiyam bhi pahley se mukhtasar tha. phir ( chotha ( rukoo kya ye bhi bahut lamba tha lekin pahley se kuchh kam . phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sajda kya aur Namaz se farigh huey to suraj saaf ho chuka tha. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutbe mein farmaya ke suraj aur chaand donon Allah Taala ki nishaniyan hain aur kisi ki maut w zindagi ki wjah se unmein girahan nahi lagta isliye jab tum ko malum ho ke girahan lag gaya hai to Allah Taala ka zikr karo. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! ham ne dekha ke (namaz mein) apni jagah se aap kuchh aagey badhey aur phir iske baad peechhey hat gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine jannat dekhi aur uska ek khosha todnaa chaha tha agar main usey tod sakta to tum usey rehti duniya tak khaatey aur mujhey jahannam bhi dikhai gaee maine us se zyada bhayanak aur khofnak manzar kabhi nahi dekha. maine dekha usmein auratein zyada hain. kisi ne puchha ya Rasulullah! uski kya wjah hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne kufr ( inkaar) ki wjah se. puchha gaya, kya Allah Taala ka kufr ( inkaar) karti hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shauhar ka aur ehsan ka kufr karti hain. zindagi bhar tum kisi aurat ke sath achchha sulook karo lekin kabhi agar koi mizaaj k khilaf baat aa gaee to fauran yahi kahegii ke maine tum se kabhi bhalai nahi dekhi."
1053,"jab suraj ko girahan laga to main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar aai. achcha log khadey huey Namaz padh rahe they aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bhi Namaz mein Sharik thi maine puchha ke logon ko baat kya pesh aaii? is par aap ne aasman ki taraf ishara karke Subhan-Allah kaha, phir maine puchha kya koi nishani hai? iska aap ne ishaare se haan mein jawab diya. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir main bhi khadi ho gaee. lekin mujhey chakkar aa gaya isliye main apne sar par pani dalney lagi jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to Allah Taala ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya ke wo cheezein jo ke maine pahley nahi dekhi thin ab unhein maine apni usi jagah se dekh liya. jannat aur dozakh tak maine dekhi aur mujhey wahiy ke zariey bataya gaya hai ke tum qabr mein dajjal ke fitne ki tarah ya (ye kaha ke) dajjal ke fitna ke qareeb aik fitne mein mubtala hogey. mujhey yad nahi ke Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kya kaha tha aap ne farmaya ke tumhen laya jaeyga aur puchha jaeyga ke us shakhs (mujh (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke barey main tum kya jantey ho. momin ya ye kaha ke yaqin karne wala (mujhey yad nahi ke un 2 baton mein se Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kon si baat kahi thi) to kahega ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey samney sahi rasta aur uske dalaayel pesh kiye aur ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par eman laey they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baat qabool ki aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ittaba (pairvi) kya tha. is par us se kaha jaeyga ke to marde-Saaleh hai to aaraam se so ja hamein to pahley hi malum tha ke to eman w yaqin wala hai. munafiq ya shak karne wala nahi (mujhey malum nahi ke Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kya kaha tha) wo ye kahega ke mujhey kuchh malum nahi maine logon se aik baat suni thi wahi maine bhi kahi (aagey mujh ko kuchh haqiqat malum nahin) ."
1054,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suraj girahan mein ghulam aazad karne ka hukm farmaayaa.
1055,"aik Yahudi aurat unke paas kuchh maangney aai. usne kaha ke aapko Allah Taala qabr ke azab se bachaaey, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke kya qabr mein bhi azab hoga? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye sun kar) farmaya ke main Allah ki us se panah mangta hun."
1056,"phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din subah ke waqt sawar huey (kahiin janey ke liye) idhar suraj girahan lag gaya isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas aa gaey, abhi chasht ka waqt tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beeviyon ke hujron se guzrey aur (masjid mein) khadey ho kar Namaz shuru kar di sahaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein saf baandh kar khadey ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qiyam bahut lamba kya, rukoo bhi bahut lamba kya phir rukoo se sar uthane ke baad dobara lamba qiyam kya lekin pahley se kam, iske baad rukoo bahut lamba kya lekin pahley rukoo se kuchh kam. phir rukoo se sar utha kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein gaey aur lamba sajda kya. phir lamba qiyam kya aur ye qiyam bhi pahley se kam tha. phir lamba rukoo kya agarche ye rukoo bhi pahley ke muqaabley mein kam tha phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukoo se khadey ho gaey aur lamba qiyam kya lekin ye qiyam phir pahley se kam tha ab (chauthaa) rukoo kya, agarche ye rukoo bhi pahley rukoo ke muqaabley mein kam tha. phir sajda kya bahut lamba lekin pahley sajde ke muqaabley mein kam. Namaz se farigh honey ke baad jo kuchh Allah Taala ne chaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya, phir logon ko samjhaayaa ke qabr ke azab se Allah ki panah maangein."
1057,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya suraj aur chaand mein girahan kisi ki maut ki wjah se nahi lagta albatta ye donon Allah Taala ki nishaniyan hain, isliye jab tum girahan dekho to Namaz padho."
1058,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein suraj ko girahan laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur logon ke sath Namaz mein mashghool ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne lambi qirat ki. phir rukoo kya aur ye bhi bahut lamba tha. phir sar uthaya aur us martaba bhi der tak qirat ki magar pehli qirat se kam. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (doosri martaba) rukoo kya bahut lamba lekin pahley ke muqable mein mukhtasar, phir rukoo se sar utha kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein chaley gaey aur 2 sajdey kiye phir khadey huey aur dusri rakaat mein bhi isi tarah kya jaisey pehli rakaat mein kar chukey they. iske baad farmaya ke suraj aur chaand mein girahan kisi ki maut w hayaat se nahi lagtaa. albatta ye donon Allah Taala ki nishaniyan hain jinhein Allah Taala apne bandon ko dikhaataa hai, isliye jab tum unhein dekho to fauran Namaz ke liye daudo."
1059,"aik baar suraj girahan hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut ghabraa kar uthey us dar se ke kahin qiyamat na qaaim ho jaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid mein aa kar bahut hi lamba qiyaam, lamba rukoo aur lambey sajdon ke sath Namaz padhi. maine kabhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is tarah kartey nahi dekha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz ke baad farmaya ke ye nishaniyan hain jinhein Allah Taala bhejta hai ye kisi ki maut aur zindagi ki wjah se nahi aatiin balke Allah Taala inke zariey apne bandon ko daraataa hai isliye jab tum is tarah ki koi cheez dekho to fauran Allah Taala ke zikr aur usse istighfar ki taraf lapko."
1060,jis din Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki maut hui suraj girahan bhi isi din laga. is par kuchh logon ne kaha ke girahan Ibrahim (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saahibzaadey) ki wafat ki wjah se laga hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se do nishan hain. unmein girahan kisi ki maut w hayaat ki wjah se nahi lagtaa. jab usey dekho to Allah paak se dua karo aur Namaz padho yahan tak ke suraj saaf ho jaey.
1061,jab suraj saaf ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba diya. pahley Allah Taala ki shaan ke mutabiq uski tareef ki iske baad farmaya (ammaa ba'd).
1062,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein suraj ko girahan laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi thi.
1063,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein suraj girahan laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni chadar ghaseet'tey huey (badii tezi se) masjid mein pahunchey. sahaba bhi jama ho gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein do rakaat Namaz padhai, girahan bhi khatm ho gaya. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain aur unmein girahan kisi ki maut par nahi lagta isliye jab girahan lagey to us waqt tak Namaz aur dua mein mashghool raho jab tak ye saaf na ho jaey. ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isliye farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik sahibzadey Ibrahim ki wafat (usi din) hui thi aur kuchh log unke mutaalliq kehney lagey they (ke girahan unki maut par laga hai)."
1064,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suraj girahan ki 2 rakaton mein char rukoo kiye aur pehli rakaat dusri rakaat se lambi thi.
1065,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne girahan ki Namaz mein qirat buland awaz se ki, qirat se farigh ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) takbeer keh kar rukoo mein chaley gaey jab rukoo se sar uthaya to ( سمع الله لمن حمده , Mina padhi. ربنا ولك الحمد‏ ( kaha phir dobara qirat shuru ki. gharaz girahan ki 2 rakaton mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char rukoo aur char sajdey kiye."
1066,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein suraj girahan laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi se elaan kara diya ke Namaz honey wali hai phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakatein char rukoo aur char sajdon ke sath padhin. Waleed-bin-muslim ne bayan kya ke mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin namr ne khabar di aur unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se suna, usi hadis ki tarah Zohri (ibne-Shahaab) ne bayan kya ke is par maine (Urwa se) puchha ke phir tumharey bhai Abdullah-bin-Zubair ne jab Madina mein (kusoof) ki Namaz padhai to kyon aisa kya ke jis tarah subah ki Namaz padhi jati hai. isi tarah ye Namaz ( kusoof ( bhi unhon-ne padhai. unhon-ne jawab diya ke yahan unhon-ne sunnat ke khilaf kya. Abdur-Rehman bin namr ke sath us hadis ko Sulaimaan-bin-Kaseer aur Sufiyaan-bin-Husain ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya, usmein bhi qirat awaz k sath karne ka bayan hai."
